title: #92Noon! Friday Football Feast!
description: PA & Charch are in studio talking everything from OTAs to colonoscopies. Wild head coach Bruce Boudreau calls in to chat about the offseason and his connections to the Stanley Cup Final. Mitch Moss from VSIN talks all things Vegas, from the Golden Knights to Golden Tee. Also, Scott Linn gives the Washington D.C. perspective on the Final and Chad Greenway swings by the studio and talks Vikings football and his future in broadcasting!
